nodes.text: The Dark Jedi Volfe Karkko was incarcerated in a temple on the prison-world of Kiffex when he was apprehended by the Jedi High Council centuries prior to the Invasion of Naboo. The temple was destroyed in 30 BBY when Jedi Knight Quinlan Vos defeated Karkko and rescued his Padawan, Aayla Secura, from the Dark Jedi's influence.
